text## Instalasi Dependencies (Sekali Saja)

```bash
# 1. Go tools (wajib untuk performa terbaik)
go install -v github.com/projectdiscovery/httpx/cmd/httpx@latest
go install -v github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei/v3/cmd/nuclei@latest
go install -v github.com/hahwul/dalfox/v2@latest
go install -v github.com/sensepost/gowitness@latest

# 2. System tools
sudo apt install nmap wafw00f -y        # Ubuntu/Debian/Kali
# brew install nmap wafw00f              # macOS

# 3. Update Nuclei templates
nuclei -update-templates
Pastikan $HOME/go/bin ada di $PATH Anda.
Cara Menggunakan
1. Campaign Penuh (Rekomendasi)
Bashchmod +x civet_launcher_pro.sh
./civet_launcher_pro.sh
Akan muncul menu interaktif:

Pilih tool atau "all"
Otomatis jalankan Civet Pro + IMDS Scanner + Domain Scanner
Hasil tersimpan rapi di folder campaign dengan timestamp

Non-interaktif:
Bash./civet_launcher_pro.sh \
    -t targets.txt \
    -w wordlists/subdomains-top10000.txt \
    -m aggressive \
    -j 20
2. Civet Pro (Recon Utama)
Bashpython3 civet_pro.py \
    -u https://example.com \
    --wordlist wordlists/subdomains-top1000.txt \
    --mode aggressive \
    -o output_example
3. IMDSv1/v2 Checker (khusus AWS SSRF)
Bashpython3 imds_scanner.py \
    -f ssrf_targets.txt \
    --aggressive \
    -o imds_results.json
4. Quick Domain Scan
Bash./upgraded-domain-scanner.sh example.com
Contoh Output Campaign
